An '''avatar raid''' is a scenario in VRChat where a small or large group of users, use an [[Avatars|avatar]], or a similar category of avatars in the same [[Instances|instance]], to entertain or annoy other users through expressive character roleplay.

== Overview ==
Any single avatar can be used for an avatar raid, or each user can choose to be a character from a certain [[Community:Anime culture in VRChat|anime]], or video game series, as an example. While there is not necessarily a goal for an avatar raid, generally, the act of roleplaying the character can be entertaining for the person in the raid, and can be more enjoyable with a group of people.

== Examples of raid avatars ==
* [[Ugandan Knuckles]]
* [[VRRat]], on [[List of April Fools' Day jokes|April Fools' Day]]
* "Kitten Marching Band" avatars
* Various animals

